# CrossGen #

Very simple tool for generating crosswords. *Almost* course work.

### Features ###

1. Supports many of languages if dictionary contains lines like
```
    WORD - DESCRIPTION
```
2. Supports any grid that have format like
```
    ++++
    +--+
    +--+
    ++++
```

### Dependecies ###
Only wxWidgets.

